HEADWORD: Macrodome
<hw>Mac"ro*dome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Macro-</ets>
+ <ets>dome</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Crystallog.)</fld> <def>A dome parallel
to the longer lateral axis of an orthorhombic crystal. See
<er>Dome</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 4.</def>⟦br⟧
